###### BlockCamp --- November 28, Paris, France

A one-day event co-organized by the Ruby-fr and Smalltalk-fr communities, and sponsorized by [ESUG][]. [More info here](http://community.ofset.org/index.php/Smalltalk_Party_Paris_2009).


###### OSDC.fr 2009 --- October 2--3, Paris, France
I attended the [Open Source Developers Conference](http://act.osdc.fr/osdc2009fr/) at at La Cité des Sciences et de l'Industrie, in Paris. Here are [my few photos of the event](http://www.flickr.com/photos/damienpollet/sets/72157622391742069/).


###### ESUG 2009 --- August 31--September 4, Brest, France.
I attended the [2009 International Smalltalk Conference][esug09] and joint workshop [IWST'09][], organized by [ESUG][]. I presented [Citezen][] to the [Innovation Technology Awards][awards]. Here are [my photos of the event](http://www.flickr.com/photos/damienpollet/collections/72157622253550888/); other photos, as well as talk slides, are available via the conference website.

